mg src=\"../../images/weixintupian_20210224160842.jpg\">\n  \n  <div class=\"current wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n<div class=\"clearfix container\">\n    <div class=\"pull-left banner-tt\">\n\n\n\n固体力学研究所</div>\n    <div class=\"pull-left nav-b\">                <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk.htm\">师资情况</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\">师资信息</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx/gclxx.htm\">工程力学系</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix container\"><ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\">\n    \n    <li><a href=\"../../szqk/ys.htm\" title=\"院士\">院士</a></li>\n\n    \n    <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\" title=\"师资信息\">师资信息</a></li>\n\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n  </div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n<div>\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format2.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff;\">\n\n       <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/6/12/6B/12A30E2566910AC50856ED19808_8532844D_13F3BF.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>徐芦平</a></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                                    <p>职称：副研究员</p>\n                                    <p>电话：010-62782426</p>\n                                  \n                    </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div> \n        <div id=\"vsb_content_2\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"></div><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<div>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">清华大学航天航空学院，微纳米力学与多学科交叉研究中心（CNMM）副研究员；</p>\n <p>“学堂计划”钱学森力学班核心组成员；</p>\n <p>行健书院副院长；</p>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:lupingxu@tsinghua.edu.cn\">lupingxu@tsinghua.edu.cn</a></p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">教育背景</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><div>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">1998-2002，北京大学物理学院，本科</p>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2002-2008，北京大学物理学院，博士</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">工作履历</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><div>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">2008-2012，法国国家健康医学研究院（INSERM）&amp; 巴黎笛卡尔大学，博士后</p>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2012-今，清华大学航天航空学院，教师</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">研究方向</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><div>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">微纳米生物技术、复杂系统演化动力学、创新教育系统工程</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">学术成果</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><div>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">[1] Xu L, Robert L, Ouyang Q, Taddei F, Chen Y, Lindner AB, Baigl D. Microcontact printing of living bacteria arrays with cellular resolution. <b>Nano Lett.</b> 2007 Jul;7(7):2068-72. doi: 10.1021/nl070983z. Epub 2007 Jun 22. PMID: 17585831.</p>\n <p>[2] Cui G, Xu Z, Li H, Zhang S, Xu L, Siria A, Ma M. Enhanced osmotic transport in individual double-walled carbon nanotube. <b>Nat Commun. </b>2023 Apr 21;14(1):2295. doi: 10.1038/s41467-023-37970-3. PMID: 37085535; PMCID: PMC10121574.</p>\n <p>[3] Yang Y, Santos AL, Xu L, Lotton C, Taddei F, Lindner AB. Temporal scaling of aging as an adaptive strategy of <i>Escherichia coli</i>.<b> Sci Adv. 2019</b> May 29;5(5):eaaw2069. doi: 10.1126/sciadv.aaw2069. PMID: 31149637; PMCID: PMC6541466.</p>\n <p>[4] Wu S, Jeffet J, Grunwald A, Sharim H, Gilat N, Torchinsky D, Zheng Q, Zirkin S, Xu L, Ebenstein Y. Microfluidic DNA combing for parallel single-molecule analysis. <b>Nanotechnology. </b>2019 Jan 25;30(4):045101. doi: 10.1088/1361-6528/aaeddc. PMID: 30485249.</p>\n <p>[5] Du J, Fan Y, Guo Z, Wang Y, Zheng X, Huang C, Liang B, Gao L, Cao Y, Chen Y, Zhang X, Li L, Xu L, Wu C, Weitz DA, Feng X. Compression Generated by a 3D Supracellular Actomyosin Cortex Promotes Embryonic Stem Cell Colony Growth and Expression of Nanog and Oct4. <b>Cell Syst.</b> 2019 Aug 28;9(2):214-220.e5. doi: 10.1016/j.cels.2019.05.008. Epub 2019 Jul 3. PMID: 31279504.</p>\n <p>[6] Liang B, Quan B, Li J, Loton C, Bredeche MF, Lindner AB, Xu L. Artificial modulation of cell width significantly affects the division time of Escherichia coli. <b>Sci Rep. 2020 </b>Oct 20;10(1):17847. doi: 10.1038/s41598-020-74778-3. PMID: 33082450; PMCID: PMC7576201.</p>\n <p>[7] Wu S, Fu T, Qiu R, Xu L. DNA fragmentation in complicated flow fields created by micro-funnel shapes. <b>Soft Matter.</b> 2021 Oct 20;17(40):9047-9056. doi: 10.1039/d1sm00984b. PMID: 34570150.</p>\n <p>[8] Wu S , Li C , Zheng Q , Xu L . Modelling DNA extension and fragmentation in contractive microfluidic devices: a Brownian dynamics and computational fluid dynamics approach. <b>Soft Matter. </b>2018 Nov 7;14(43):8780-8791. doi: 10.1039/c8sm00863a. PMID: 30338769.</p>\n <p>[9] Chen P, Xu L, Liu J, Hol FJ, Keymer JE, Taddei F, Han D, Lindner AB. Nanoscale probing the kinetics of oriented bacterial cell growth using atomic force microscopy.<b> Small. </b>2014 Aug 13;10(15):3018-25. doi: 10.1002/smll.201303724. Epub 2014 Apr 6. PMID: 24706390.</p>\n <p>[10] Sun M, Luo C, Xu L, Ji H, Ouyang Q, Yu D, Chen Y. Artificial lotus leaf by nanocasting. <b>Langmuir.</b> 2005 Sep 13;21(19):8978-81. doi: 10.1021/la050316q. PMID: 16142987.</p>\n <p>[11] 郑泉水, 徐芦平, 白峰杉等. 从星星之火到燎原之势——拔尖创新人才培养的范式探索[J/OL]. 中国科学院院刊, 2021, 36(5): 580-588. DOI:10.16418/j.issn.1000-3045.20210410001.</p>\n <p>[12] 李曼丽, 王金羽, 郑泉水等. 新时期本科教育拔尖创新人才培养模式探索－一项关于清华“钱班”12年试点的质性研究[J/OL]. Xue bao. Huadong shifan daxue xuebao / Jiao yu ke xue ban, 2022, 40(8): 031-043. DOI:10.16382/j.cnki.1000-5560.2022.08.004.</p>\n <p>[13] 李俊峰, 徐芦平, 苏芃 理工衔接 强基致远 培养可堪大任的创新人才——以清华大学行健书院为例[J/OL]. 中国大学教学, 2022(10): 4-10. DOI:10.3969/j.issn.1005-0450.2022.10.002.</p>\n <p>[14] 徐芦平 Wiser-U：探索创新人才培养的“大学2.0”模式[J/OL]. 中国教育网络, 2012(5): 59-60. DOI:10.3969/j.issn.1672-9781.2012.05.040.</p>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">[15] 郑泉水 白峰杉 苏芃 徐芦平 陈常青 清华大学钱学森力学班本科荣誉学位项目的探索[J]. 中国大学教学, 2016(8): 50-54.</p>\n</div></div></div>\n\n     </div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"friends-box wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"friends-left\">友情链接</div>\n    <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1696534067, 71220)\">清华大学</a>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"pull-left footer-logo\">                            <img src=\"../../images/logo.png\">\n</div>\n        <div class=\"pull-right footer-txt\"><!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<p>版权所有 © 清华大学京ICP备15006448号 京公网安备 110402430053 号&nbsp;</p><p>推荐ie8以上谷歌等浏览器浏览网页</p><p>联系方式：电话：010-62782434&nbsp; &nbsp;传真：010-62792407</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n<script src=\"../../